{"tid":1363564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：星期六一定要在元朗攞個威，畀位英國首相入啊，唔係對唔住自己！","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:45:13.000Z","uid":2748,"like":32,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc12c60ec2dc47b13817ca00916483a634151639","tid":1363564,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"陳雲：CNN都叫Liberate Hong Kong呀。我們在G20的口號發揮功效啦。另外，CNN質疑中英主權移交並無諮詢香港本土人，故此可以推翻啊！<br />\n好堅啊。成份CNN在宣傳《香港城邦論》的香港主權懸空論，配合英國狂人首相上任。星期六一定要在元朗攞個威，畀位英國首相入啊，唔係對唔住自己！<br />\n<br />\n屌那媽，成份CNN在宣傳《香港城邦論》，好堅啊。配合英國狂人首相上任。(Why Hong Kong's young protesters feel they're running out of time in fight for democracy)<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/07/25/asia/hong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=a3146b1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F25%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=89d3ea0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/07/25/asia/hong-kong-china-2047-protests-intl-hnk/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"51f42f2ed1e3ad8813db40ba9d86edaeecb62c37","tid":1363564,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad80adb7fe8bb9189640dcc7d853a2be4769c54","tid":1363564,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":33,"score":-33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去元朗咪中計囉on9又推人去死"},{"pid":"31c3b71ab2fb9e185a9acdddaaef5ccafb44b29f","tid":1363564,"uid":144522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo